Package proteomicsdb.org.requesttool.model.request

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    RequestListener
    The interface an observer of a RequestNotifier has to implement.
    RequestNotifier
    The interface the subjects of the observer pattern have to implement.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    RequestHandler
    Request Handler is the class that takes care of handling the connection, getting the received data into an intern data format and writing the data.
    RequestThreadPool
    The ThreadPoolExecutor that contains all requests, manages, that at most 4 of them are executed at once, and that listens to all updates.
    RunnableRequestHandler
    The runnable version of the RequestHandler.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    RequestEvent
    An enum, that contains all possible values of the state of the RequestHandler.
